<h1>About This Website</h1>

<p>DC Robotics differs from most school programs in that students don't get regularly scheduled class time to work on their creations.  As such, teams must organize themselves, working toward a common goal despite working at different times.  Conveniently enough, the internet is everywhere, and for modern students, it's a logical and intuitive place to collaborate and share ideas.  This site was originally created to provide a more specific place for that collaboration. </p>

